(*VB[*)BoxForm`temporalStorage$177254(*,*)(*"1:"*)(*]VB*)

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
Now evaluate the state infinitely and watch the result live:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Now evaluate the state infinitely and watch the result live:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Refresh[(state=mj`Propagate[state])//mj`GetArray//ArrayPlot, 1/30.0]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
To export the animation use `Image` wrapper:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
To export the animation use `Image` wrapper:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Table[ImageResize[
  Image[(
    state=mj`Propagate[state];
    state=mj`Propagate[state];
    state=mj`Propagate[state]
  )//mj`GetArray], {350,350}, Method->"NearestNeighbor"], {250}];
Export["ex.gif", AnimatedImage[%, FrameRate->25]]

